Main script:

```text
/fs04/scratch2/qb48/chikayoh/xspecies_stage1order_white3_pipeline_20260621/tscore_from_hctsa_v4.m
```

Required environment variables:

```text
HCTSA_DIR
SESSION_NAME
OUT_DIR
OUTPUT_PREFIX
LABEL_STATUS
LABEL_ISSUE_TYPE
SOURCE_RULE_NOTE
APPLY_REORDER_RULE
NORM_VAR_PREFERENCE
MAX_CHANNELS
MIN_VALID_N
MIN_DENOM
VAR_EPS
TREAT_NONFINITE_AS_NAN
```

Core settings used in 403 regression:

```text
LABEL_STATUS=verified
LABEL_ISSUE_TYPE=corrected_relabelled_source
APPLY_REORDER_RULE=none
NORM_VAR_PREFERENCE=TS_Normalised,TS_Normalized
MAX_CHANNELS=0
